| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1312 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 88f9cfa3-9abd-520a-afe8-d9688cbeabb6"
